Package: fepsfrontieR
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of fixed-effect panel stochastic frontier models by MLE
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Oliver Dippel, Clemens Haerder
Maintainer: The package maintainer <clemens.haerder@gmail.com>
Description: Esimation of fixed-effect panel stochastic frontier models by
    whitin or first difference transformation as proposed by Wang & Ho (13. January 2010).
    Maximum Likelihood Estimation is numerically computed using nlminb( ).
    Standard Errors are provided using the Hessian Matrix or
    by individual Bootstrapping.
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Clemens Haerder <clemens.haerder@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
    "Oliver Dippel <oliverdippel@gmx.de>  [aut, cre]"))
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
