    dplyr (>= 0.7.6),
    stats (>= 3.4.2),
    numDeriv (>= 2016.8-1),
    parallel (>= 3.4.2)
Suggests:
    testthat,
    MASS (>= 7.3.0)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.0),
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
